  <brief_title>Physical Activity for Improving Quality of Life and Reducing Frailty in Advanced Age</brief_title>
  <official_title>Physical Activity for Improving Quality of Life and Reducing Frailty in Advanced Age: Individually Tailored Program vs the General Guidelines Recommended by Offical Health Organizations.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
